{
  "video_id": "sVtIuDKFO1c",
  "title": "A summer school kids actually want to attend | Karim Abouelnaga",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13100.0,
      "end_time": 15120.0,
      "text": "Getting a college education"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15145.0,
      "end_time": 17300.0,
      "text": "is a 20-year investment."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18220.0,
      "end_time": 19875.0,
      "text": "When you&#39;re growing up poor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19900.0,
      "end_time": 22836.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re not accustomed to thinking that far ahead."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22860.0,
      "end_time": 26195.0,
      "text": "Instead, you&#39;re thinking about where you&#39;re going to get your next meal"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26220.0,
      "end_time": 29760.0,
      "text": "and how your family is going to pay rent that month."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29100.0,
      "end_time": 32236.0,
      "text": "Besides, my parents and my friends&#39; parents"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 35900.0,
      "text": "seemed to be doing just fine driving taxis and working as janitors."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36740.0,
      "end_time": 38636.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t until I was a teenager"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38660.0,
      "end_time": 41139.0,
      "text": "when I realized I didn&#39;t want to do those things."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41940.0,
      "end_time": 45556.0,
      "text": "By then, I was two-thirds of the way through my education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45580.0,
      "end_time": 47900.0,
      "text": "and it was almost too late to turn things around."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49500.0,
      "end_time": 51820.0,
      "text": "When you grow up poor, you want to be rich."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52620.0,
      "end_time": 53820.0,
      "text": "I was no different."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54420.0,
      "end_time": 56156.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m the second-oldest of seven,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56180.0,
      "end_time": 58596.0,
      "text": "and was raised by a single mother on government aid"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58620.0,
      "end_time": 59820.0,
      "text": "in Queens, New York."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60540.0,
      "end_time": 62476.0,
      "text": "By virtue of growing up low-income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62500.0,
      "end_time": 64836.0,
      "text": "my siblings and I went to some of New York City&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64860.0,
      "end_time": 66380.0,
      "text": "most struggling public schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 67200.0,
      "end_time": 70220.0,
      "text": "I had over 60 absences when I was in seventh grade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 71100.0,
      "end_time": 73100.0,
      "text": "because I didn&#39;t feel like going to class."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73700.0,
      "end_time": 76756.0,
      "text": "My high school had a 55 percent graduation rate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76779.0,
      "end_time": 78760.0,
      "text": "and even worse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78100.0,
      "end_time": 80396.0,
      "text": "only 20 percent of the kids graduating"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80420.0,
      "end_time": 81620.0,
      "text": "were college-ready."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82780.0,
      "end_time": 84916.0,
      "text": "When I actually did make it to college,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 84940.0,
      "end_time": 86356.0,
      "text": "I told my friend Brennan"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 86380.0,
      "end_time": 90760.0,
      "text": "how our teachers would always ask us to raise our hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90100.0,
      "end_time": 92100.0,
      "text": "if we were going to college."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 93220.0,
      "end_time": 94956.0,
      "text": "I was taken aback when Brennan said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94980.0,
      "end_time": 97660.0,
      "text": "\"Karim, I&#39;ve never been asked that question before.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98540.0,
      "end_time": 101516.0,
      "text": "It was always, \"What college are you going to?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 101540.0,
      "end_time": 103476.0,
      "text": "Just the way that question is phrased"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 103500.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "made it unacceptable for him not to have gone to college."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 107780.0,
      "end_time": 109820.0,
      "text": "Nowadays I get asked a different question."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 110500.0,
      "end_time": 112780.0,
      "text": "\"How were you able to make it out?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113580.0,
      "end_time": 115940.0,
      "text": "For years I said I was lucky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117140.0,
      "end_time": 118340.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s not just luck."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 119100.0,
      "end_time": 121675.0,
      "text": "When my older brother and I graduated from high school"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121700.0,
      "end_time": 122956.0,
      "text": "at the very same time"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 122980.0,
      "end_time": 125196.0,
      "text": "and he later dropped out of a two-year college,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 125220.0,
      "end_time": 127676.0,
      "text": "I wanted to understand why he dropped out"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 127700.0,
      "end_time": 128900.0,
      "text": "and I kept studying."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 130600.0,
      "end_time": 133436.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t until I got to Cornell as a Presidential Research Scholar"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 133460.0,
      "end_time": 137196.0,
      "text": "that I started to learn about the very real educational consequences"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137220.0,
      "end_time": 139995.0,
      "text": "of being raised by a single mother on government aid"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 140190.0,
      "end_time": 141820.0,
      "text": "and attending the schools that I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 142739.0,
      "end_time": 146580.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s when my older brother&#39;s trajectory began to make complete sense to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 148100.0,
      "end_time": 151476.0,
      "text": "I also learned that our most admirable education reformers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 151500.0,
      "end_time": 155156.0,
      "text": "people like Arne Duncan, the former US Secretary of Education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 155180.0,
      "end_time": 157876.0,
      "text": "or Wendy Kopp, the founder of Teach For America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 157900.0,
      "end_time": 160700.0,
      "text": "had never attended an inner city public school like I had."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 161340.0,
      "end_time": 165156.0,
      "text": "So much of our education reform is driven by a sympathetic approach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 165180.0,
      "end_time": 166436.0,
      "text": "where people are saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 166460.0,
      "end_time": 169476.0,
      "text": "\"Let&#39;s go and help these poor inner city kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 169500.0,
      "end_time": 171500.0,
      "text": "or these poor black and Latino kids,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 172140.0,
      "end_time": 174516.0,
      "text": "instead of an empathetic approach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 174540.0,
      "end_time": 177956.0,
      "text": "where someone like me, who had grown up in this environment, could say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 177980.0,
      "end_time": 180196.0,
      "text": "\"I know the adversities that you&#39;re facing"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 180220.0,
      "end_time": 182600.0,
      "text": "and I want to help you overcome them.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 183380.0,
      "end_time": 186760.0,
      "text": "Today when I get questions about how I made it out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 186100.0,
      "end_time": 188596.0,
      "text": "I share that one of the biggest reasons"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 188620.0,
      "end_time": 190700.0,
      "text": "is that I wasn&#39;t ashamed to ask for help."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 191660.0,
      "end_time": 194276.0,
      "text": "In a typical middle class or affluent household,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 194300.0,
      "end_time": 196760.0,
      "text": "if a kid is struggling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 196100.0,
      "end_time": 200360.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a good chance that a parent or a teacher will come to their rescue"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 200600.0,
      "end_time": 201996.0,
      "text": "even if they don&#39;t ask for help."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 202200.0,
      "end_time": 204156.0,
      "text": "However, if that same kid is growing up poor"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 204180.0,
      "end_time": 205420.0,
      "text": "and doesn&#39;t ask for help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 206600.0,
      "end_time": 208380.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a good chance that no one will help them."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 208700.0,
      "end_time": 211700.0,
      "text": "There are virtually no social safety nets available."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 212980.0,
      "end_time": 214356.0,
      "text": "So seven years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 214380.0,
      "end_time": 217196.0,
      "text": "I started to reform our public education system"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 217220.0,
      "end_time": 219540.0,
      "text": "shaped by my firsthand perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 220780.0,
      "end_time": 222352.0,
      "text": "And I started with summer school."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 223780.0,
      "end_time": 227116.0,
      "text": "Research tells us that two-thirds of the achievement gap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 227140.0,
      "end_time": 229476.0,
      "text": "which is the disparity in educational attainment"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 229500.0,
      "end_time": 231676.0,
      "text": "between rich kids and poor kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 231700.0,
      "end_time": 233835.0,
      "text": "or black kids and white kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 233860.0,
      "end_time": 236540.0,
      "text": "could be directly attributed to the summer learning loss."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 237460.0,
      "end_time": 240276.0,
      "text": "In low-income neighborhoods, kids forget almost three months"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 240300.0,
      "end_time": 242356.0,
      "text": "of what they learned during the school year"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 242380.0,
      "end_time": 243716.0,
      "text": "over the summer."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 243740.0,
      "end_time": 245356.0,
      "text": "They return to school in the fall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 245380.0,
      "end_time": 247436.0,
      "text": "and their teachers spend another two months"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 247460.0,
      "end_time": 248876.0,
      "text": "reteaching them old material."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 248900.0,
      "end_time": 250396.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s five months."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 250420.0,
      "end_time": 253360.0,
      "text": "The school year in the United States is only 10 months."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 253600.0,
      "end_time": 255676.0,
      "text": "If kids lose five months of learning every single year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 255700.0,
      "end_time": 257180.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s half of their education."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 257940.0,
      "end_time": 259140.0,
      "text": "Half."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 259899.0,
      "end_time": 263600.0,
      "text": "If kids were in school over the summer, then they couldn&#39;t regress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 263820.0,
      "end_time": 266140.0,
      "text": "but traditional summer school is poorly designed."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 266740.0,
      "end_time": 268796.0,
      "text": "For kids it feels like punishment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 268820.0,
      "end_time": 270860.0,
      "text": "and for teachers it feels like babysitting."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 272140.0,
      "end_time": 276156.0,
      "text": "But how can we expect principals to execute an effective summer program"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 276180.0,
      "end_time": 278636.0,
      "text": "when the school year ends the last week of June"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 278660.0,
      "end_time": 281200.0,
      "text": "and then summer school starts just one week later?"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 281780.0,
      "end_time": 284356.0,
      "text": "There just isn&#39;t enough time to find the right people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 284380.0,
      "end_time": 285635.0,
      "text": "sort out the logistics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 285660.0,
      "end_time": 289860.0,
      "text": "and design an engaging curriculum that excites kids and teachers."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 291580.0,
      "end_time": 295556.0,
      "text": "But what if we created a program over the summer"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 295580.0,
      "end_time": 299276.0,
      "text": "that empowered teachers as teaching coaches"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 299300.0,
      "end_time": 301300.0,
      "text": "to develop aspiring educators?"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 302540.0,
      "end_time": 305276.0,
      "text": "What if we empowered college-educated role models"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 305300.0,
      "end_time": 306580.0,
      "text": "as teaching fellows"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 307380.0,
      "end_time": 309916.0,
      "text": "to help kids realize their college ambitions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 309940.0,
      "end_time": 312195.0,
      "text": "What if empowered high-achieving kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 312220.0,
      "end_time": 315636.0,
      "text": "as mentors to tutor their younger peers"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 315660.0,
      "end_time": 317980.0,
      "text": "and inspire them to invest in their education?"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 319460.0,
      "end_time": 323195.0,
      "text": "What if we empowered all kids as scholars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 323220.0,
      "end_time": 326436.0,
      "text": "asked them what colleges they were going to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 326460.0,
      "end_time": 329419.0,
      "text": "designed a summer school they want to attend"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 330220.0,
      "end_time": 332756.0,
      "text": "to completely eliminate the summer learning loss"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 332780.0,
      "end_time": 334979.0,
      "text": "and close two-thirds of the achievement gap?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 337100.0,
      "end_time": 341716.0,
      "text": "By this summer, my team will have served over 4,000 low-income children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 341740.0,
      "end_time": 344676.0,
      "text": "trained over 300 aspiring teachers"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 344700.0,
      "end_time": 346996.0,
      "text": "and created more than 1,000 seasonal jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 347200.0,
      "end_time": 350600.0,
      "text": "across some of New York City&#39;s most disadvantaged neighborhoods."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 350820.0,
      "end_time": 354620.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 356660.0,
      "end_time": 358996.0,
      "text": "And our kids are succeeding."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 359200.0,
      "end_time": 360996.0,
      "text": "Two years of independent evaluations"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 361200.0,
      "end_time": 363955.0,
      "text": "tell us that our kids eliminate the summer learning loss"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 363980.0,
      "end_time": 366156.0,
      "text": "and make growth of one month in math"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 366180.0,
      "end_time": 367420.0,
      "text": "and two months in reading."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 368200.0,
      "end_time": 371515.0,
      "text": "So instead of returning to school in the fall three months behind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 371540.0,
      "end_time": 374180.0,
      "text": "they now go back four months ahead in math"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 375380.0,
      "end_time": 377436.0,
      "text": "and five months ahead in reading."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 377460.0,
      "end_time": 380859.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 384580.0,
      "end_time": 386515.0,
      "text": "Ten years ago, if you would have told me"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 386540.0,
      "end_time": 390716.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;d graduate in the top 10 percent of my class from an Ivy League institution"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 390740.0,
      "end_time": 394716.0,
      "text": "and have an opportunity to make a dent on our public education system"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 394740.0,
      "end_time": 397780.0,
      "text": "just by tackling two months of the calendar year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 398500.0,
      "end_time": 400236.0,
      "text": "I would have said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
